e]]\n|February 27, 1968 \u2013 August 22, 1969\n|3\n|542\n|- align=center\n|4\n|align=left | {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Rub\u00e9n Olivares]]\n|August 22, 1969 \u2013 October 16, 1970\n|2\n|420\n|- align=center\n|5\n|align=left | {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Chucho Castillo]]\n|October 16, 1970 \u2013 April 2, 1971\n|0\n|168\n|- align=center\n|6\n|align=left | {{flagicon|MEX}} Rub\u00e9n Olivares (2)\n|April 2, 1971 \u2013 March 19, 1972\n|2\n|352\n|- align=center\n|7\n|align=left | {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Rafael Herrera]]\n|March 19, 1972 \u2013 July 29, 1972\n|0\n|132\n|- align=center\n|8\n|align=left | {{flagicon|PAN}} [[Enrique Pinder]]\n|July 29, 1972 \u2013 January 20, 1973\n|0\n|175\n|- align=center\n|9\n|align=left | {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Romeo Anaya]]\n|January 20, 1973 \u2013 November 3, 1973\n|2\n|287\n|- align=center\n|10\n|align=left | {{flagicon|RSA|1928}} [[Arnold Taylor]]\n|November 3, 1973 \u2013 July 3, 1974\n|0\n|242\n|- align=center\n|11\n|align=left | {{flagicon|KOR|1949}} [[Hong Soo-hwan]]\n|July 3, 1974 \u2013 March 14, 1975\n|1\n|254\n|- align=center\n|12\n|align=left | {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Alfonso Zamora]]\n|March 14, 1975 \u2013 November 19, 1977\n|5\n|981\n|- align=center\n|13\n|align=left | {{flagicon|PAN}} [[Jorge Luj\u00e1n (boxer)|Jorge Luj\u00e1n]]\n|November 19, 1977 \u2013 August 29, 1980\n|5\n|style=\"background:#dfffdf;\"|1014\n|- align=center\n|14\n|align=left | {{flagicon|PUR|1952}} [[Julian Sol\u00eds]]\n|August 29, 1980 \u2013 November 14, 1980\n|0\n|77\n|- align=center\n|15\n|align=left | {{flagicon|USA}} [[Jeff Chandler (boxer)|Jeff Chandler]]\n|November 14, 1980 \u2013 April 7, 1984\n|9\n|style=\"background:#dfdfdf;\"|1240\n|- align=center\n|16\n|align=left | {{flagicon|USA}} [[Richie Sandoval]]\n|April 7, 1984 \u2013 March 10, 1986\n|2\n|702\n|- align=center\n|17\n|align=left | {{flagicon|USA}} [[Gaby Canizales]]\n|March 10, 1986 \u2013 June 4, 1986\n|0\n|86\n|- align=center\n|18\n|align=left | {{flagicon|VEN|1954}} [[Bernardo Pinango]]\n|June 4, 198